{"tid":125441,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天選舉呈請法援上訴申請成功","createTime":"2017-02-18T13:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T06:50:35.000Z","uid":48,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa1e33db84f1f347ab696a070eb9933e16b6e88","tid":125441,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"民族黨召集人陳浩天昨日 (17/2) 接獲律師通知，其選舉呈請的法律援助申請上訴成功，將會獲批法援，進行就被選舉主任取消2016年立法會選舉參選資格而提出的選舉呈請。<br />\n<br />\n法律援助署月前於徵詢一名資深大律師的法律意見後，決定拒絕陳浩天的法援申請。然而，審理上訴的高等法院聆案官認為，按法援的審批準則，即是否有合理機會勝訴，陳浩天的選舉呈請符合申請要求，故批准陳浩天的上訴。<br />\n敝黨歡迎法院裁決，會繼續進行選舉呈請，以不斷擴大殖民政府的憲制危機，並努力推動香港民族運動，務必令殖民政府威權殆盡，節節敗退，永不翻身。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/a.472253396306953.1073741828.468882569977369/610187279180230/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fphotos%2Fa.472253396306953.1073741828.468882569977369%2F610187279180230%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=41f0c12e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/a.472253396306953.1073741828.468882569977369/610187279180230/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"fb7133e37efd3f2ff1ee3f2cce9c954abf45e66b","tid":125441,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03a6299e08435dcc326ebec72b1d3300803bd1f","tid":125441,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"都過唔到DQ啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9d00dc950416524a0555d4bfe12b4d4d508ec2","tid":125441,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都過唔到DQ啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地都唔在乎個議席<br />\n<br />\n你估人地好似梁天琦咁咩<br />\n攛爛塊臉都要躝入去<